insights.text: Vuori is uniquely balanced: 40% women's / 43% men's. Alo skews 52% women's, Gymshark 25% men's.
Vuori's earth tone palette (16%) is +9% vs industry avgreinforcing California lifestyle positioning.
Jogger battle: Vuori (130) vs Lululemon (93). Vuori leads by 37.
Neutrals (black/white/gray/navy) = 50% of Vuori's palette. Core basics that drive repeat purchases.
Vuori leads Lululemon in men's: 1118 vs 727 products. A 54% advantage.
Vuori ranks #2 in shorts with 413 products. Behind Gymshark (702).
Outerwear depth: Vuori has 386 products vs Lululemon's 244. Key for cooler weather expansion.
Market context: 14,016 competitor products tracked. Vuori's 2,609 = 16% share of tracked catalog.
